---
title: Sweet Pepper-Stuffed Chicken with Roasted Broccoli and Potatoes
description: Quick, simple and tasty is the order of the day for this recipe. Using a delicious combination of mozzarella, roasted red peppers and basil for the stuffing, every bite of chicken gets a little extra hit of flavour.
